  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> One of the apparitions you are attuned to grants Heraldry Lore or Underworld Lore as an apparition skill.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You channel the spiritual power of ancient rivalries or spiteful grudges into a devastating attack. Make a melee Strike against a creature within your reach. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to this attack and deal an additional @Damage[2d6[negative]] damage to the target; if the target is undead, this Strike instead deals an additional @Damage[2d6[positive]] damage. This ability gains the vitality trait if it deals vitality damage, or the void trait if it deals void damage.</p>"
    },
